articles.title: Russian designer dubbed the 'Soviet Christian Dior' dies at age 85 - Daily Mail
articles.description: Owner of fashion label Slava Zaitsev, Viacheslav Zaitsev, who was diagnosed with Parkinson's disease in 2016, passed away today, according to Russian media.
articles.content:
